WOMAN 1: Are you okay?

02:06.209 --> 02:07.949
WOMAN 2: Help her.
You okay?

02:08.170 --> 02:11.503
Please help me!
Please, I need help. Please.

02:14.509 --> 02:16.374
[BOY SCREAMING]

02:16.553 --> 02:19.044
[PEOPLE TALKING INDISTINCTLY]

